accessibility.text: Creating a fluid and seamless experience was the goal of this exercise. Also, I wanted to leverage animation when necessary.
The cinematic adds a layer of meaning that is subtle and vibrant. It allows the user to understand better the process and drives the focus on relevant areas.
Ultimately, I wanted the user to feel rewarded during the whole journey. Delivering on each step of the experience a sense of wonder and satisfaction.
You’ve got question. Voice has answers
